title: Episode 353: Young Gummy (Feat. Saucy Santana)
itunes:title: Episode 353: Young Gummy (Feat. Saucy Santana)
description:
Rapper, Saucy Santana joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get WILD! We discuss a whole range of topics including saying "I love you" after the first date, why Saucy hates anal sex, getting outed by his cousin, and much more! Saucy also breaks down why the prank wars on tour weren't funny to him, and he even gives his perspective on Florida's "Don't Say Gay" bill. Enjoy!
